          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer21274295" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer443200052489957777">A wonderful classic of dark fantasy; every short story in this collection is a small jewel. Comparable in quality and prose to Angela Carter&apos;s The Bloody Chamber of which I&apos;m confident Lee was heavily indebted to.</span>
  <span id="freeText443200052489957777" style="display:none">A wonderful classic of dark fantasy; every short story in this collection is a small jewel. Comparable in quality and prose to Angela Carter's The Bloody Chamber of which I'm confident Lee was heavily indebted to.</span>
  <a data-text-id="443200052489957777" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


